00:32:58,719 --> 00:33:03,129
In the night because this guru, his limbs
are broken and hands are broken, so he goes

448
00:33:03,129 --> 00:33:04,129
on a tiger.

449
00:33:04,129 --> 00:33:06,940
So he said, “And this tiger came and pushed
me into a ghat!

450
00:33:06,940 --> 00:33:12,840
And I was lying there about thirteen, fourteen
feet down below, and this guru after three,

451
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:19,749
four days lowered down some rotis, some breads
to me, and he said, “Now eat it and stay

452
00:33:19,749 --> 00:33:20,749
there.

453
00:33:20,749 --> 00:33:24,229
And till you promise me that you will not
go and trouble Mataji, I am not going to take

454
00:33:24,229 --> 00:33:26,169
you out of this place!”

455
00:33:26,169 --> 00:33:29,919
And then after two days he sent a few people
to pick him up and brought.

456
00:33:29,919 --> 00:33:33,590
He said, “I am not here to take money from
you.

457
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:35,289
You cannot give me money, anything.

458
00:33:35,289 --> 00:33:37,249
But I will only teach you a good lesson!”

459
00:33:37,249 --> 00:33:39,389
He said, “I have had enough of it."

460
00:33:39,389 --> 00:33:43,759
He said, “Now you take these legs around
your neck, go dangling to Mataji, and She’s

461
00:33:43,759 --> 00:33:44,929
going to cure you.

462
00:33:44,929 --> 00:33:46,369
I am not going to cure you.

463
00:33:46,369 --> 00:33:48,950
And don’t come and tell me stories!”

464
00:33:48,950 --> 00:33:52,349
“Oh God” I said, “Look at this,” then
of course we tried and worked on him, that’s

465
00:33:52,349 --> 00:33:53,349
a different point.

466
00:33:53,349 --> 00:33:54,349
But this is what it is.

467
00:33:54,349 --> 00:33:57,519
He said he wants technique, so he gave him
a technique.

468
00:33:57,519 --> 00:34:03,080
Another fellow who was like this, a doctor,
he was troubling me, and I didn’t tell him,

469
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:05,549
but he felt that he should go and see this
guru.

470
00:34:05,549 --> 00:34:10,270
And for one month he made this fellow clean
a Shiva’s temple, taking the water seven

471
00:34:10,270 --> 00:34:13,750
miles every day, morning and evening: with
one bucket cleaning in Shiva’s temple!

472
00:34:13,750 --> 00:34:17,810
And doctor came back, he was so thinned down,
absolutely exhausted.

473
00:34:17,810 --> 00:34:20,629
I said, “What’s the matter?”

474
00:34:20,629 --> 00:34:23,059
He said, “I was cleaning Shiva’s temple
for a month!”

475
00:34:23,059 --> 00:34:26,639
So when I met this guru I asked him, “Why
did you do that to him?”

476
00:34:26,639 --> 00:34:27,990
He said, “For a donkey, you better give
donkey’s job!

477
00:34:27,990 --> 00:34:29,620
It’s no use telling them something of the
higher life.

478
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:32,070
They don’t want it.

479
00:34:32,070 --> 00:34:34,510
They want donkey’s life.

480
00:34:34,510 --> 00:34:39,659
So let them jump and do what they like.

481
00:34:39,659 --> 00:34:42,299
Let them be donkeys.

482
00:34:42,299 --> 00:34:45,990
Why should You try to give them [everything]
so simple?”

483
00:34:45,990 --> 00:34:46,990
I was amazed at him.

484
00:34:46,990 --> 00:34:49,560
He said, “Mother, you are a Mother and you
do what you like because this is your whim.

485
00:34:49,560 --> 00:34:52,799
But as far as we are concerned we are not
going to give Realisation to anyone.

486
00:34:52,799 --> 00:34:55,129
I have given it to one, and he’s become
a hopeless man."

487
00:34:55,129 --> 00:35:02,150
So I went to see this gentleman one day, the
one who took twenty-five years to get his

488
00:35:02,150 --> 00:35:03,150
Realisation.

489
00:35:03,150 --> 00:35:06,440
And because somebody, one of my disciples
had to invite him.

490
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:11,170
Now this fellow was smoking cigarettes like
this, sitting before me and he was talking

491
00:35:11,170 --> 00:35:16,599
quite a lot, and there were girls and women
pressing his feet and doing all kinds of things.

492
00:35:16,599 --> 00:35:19,170
Of course he got up, touched my feet.

493
00:35:19,170 --> 00:35:23,240
He sat down, then he started saying that,
“Now why this [Gagangiri] Maharaj is coming

494
00:35:23,240 --> 00:35:24,730
to see you in Bombay?

495
00:35:24,730 --> 00:35:26,240
After all he should not leave his place.

496
00:35:26,240 --> 00:35:29,059
He has been there for a hundred and eight
years,” this, that.

497
00:35:29,059 --> 00:35:32,740
I said, “Who are you to judge him?

498
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:33,780
Why are you judging him?

499
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,780
He’s your guru.

500
00:35:34,780 --> 00:35:35,780
Why should you judge him?

501
00:35:35,780 --> 00:35:36,780
He has given you Realisation."

502
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:37,780
“Yes, yes, he’s given me Realisation,
I know.

503
00:35:37,780 --> 00:35:38,780
But I can also tell him something."

504
00:35:38,780 --> 00:35:39,930
I said, “But what about your smoking?

505
00:35:39,930 --> 00:35:41,160
You are still on with the smoking."

506
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:42,630
“Oh, I don’t care.

507
00:35:42,630 --> 00:35:44,090
I am beyond everything!”

508
00:35:44,090 --> 00:35:45,560
I said, “All right."

509
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:48,540
Then I sat down watching him for a while.

510
00:35:48,540 --> 00:35:52,920
I said, “Now I am going home."

511
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:53,920
I said, “You apply this tika to me."

512
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,630
I said, “All right, first I will apply,”
so I applied [to] him.

513
00:35:55,630 --> 00:36:00,240
I said, “Now you apply,” and I sucked
his finger, this is Agnya’s finger of ego.

514
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:05,060
I sucked his finger on my Agnya, and he went
on “Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha!” like that.

515
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:06,060
He said, “Mother, Mother, Mother what you
are doing?”

516
00:36:06,060 --> 00:36:08,420
I said, “Nothing, nothing.

517
00:36:08,420 --> 00:36:10,170
You are great, you are a realised-soul.

518
00:36:10,170 --> 00:36:11,710
Why should you shake before me?

519
00:36:11,710 --> 00:36:12,740
Why are you shaking?

520
00:36:12,740 --> 00:36:13,849
Why don’t you get all right?

521
00:36:13,849 --> 00:36:14,849
Why are you shaking?”

522
00:36:14,849 --> 00:36:16,420
He said, “No, no, no please stop it, stop
it."

523
00:36:16,420 --> 00:36:21,119
I said, “Now, first promise that you are
not going to talk ill of your guru and stop

524
00:36:21,119 --> 00:36:24,299
all this nonsense of having women around and
making money!”

525
00:36:24,299 --> 00:36:29,799
But then the person with whom he went, he
swindled them completely, just imagine!

526
00:36:29,799 --> 00:36:35,180
And I asked this gentleman who met me at the
airport, “Why did you give money to this

527
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:36,180
man?”

528
00:36:36,180 --> 00:36:39,920
They said, “Mother, because he said, ‘See,
I was shaking before Mother because I was

529
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:40,920
giving power to Her!’”

530
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:41,920
I said, “Such fools!

531
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:42,920
Why did you give him the money?

532
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:45,200
Why didn’t you ask me what was happening?”

533
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:48,819
This is what it is.

534
00:36:48,819 --> 00:36:55,010
When you want technique, then in the market
there are thousand and one to give you technique,

535
00:36:55,010 --> 00:36:56,010
anything.

536
00:36:56,010 --> 00:36:59,200
They may tell you that put this [candle] on
your head, light this, and walk on the street.

537
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:01,779
And you will find thousands of them walking
like this, and the price of this [candle]

538
00:37:01,779 --> 00:37:05,650
will go up in the market, and people will
be doing it.

539
00:37:05,650 --> 00:37:12,309
Any sort of nonsense they will give you, they
would like to do it!

540
00:37:12,309 --> 00:37:18,940
For example, these people at Oxford Street:
they are standing there, [the] Hareramas.

541
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:25,430
They had cleaned their hair completely and
applied those, what we call them shendis in

542
00:37:25,430 --> 00:37:27,530
India, I don’t know what you call.

543
00:37:27,530 --> 00:37:30,990
And they are sold in the market; do you know?

544
00:37:30,990 --> 00:37:32,920
Like all other wigs, they are sold as wigs
there, and that is to applied there.

545
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:33,920
And when they were dancing that was falling
down, you know!

546
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:38,599
And the dress and sari they were wearing was
also falling down!

547
00:37:38,599 --> 00:37:40,359
And such foolish people.

548
00:37:40,359 --> 00:37:41,980
I said, “What do they think?

549
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:44,830
By doing this, are they going to get God?”

550
00:37:44,830 --> 00:37:52,140
I said, “But why don’t you sit down and
receive the blessings and why to do [this]?”

551
00:37:52,140 --> 00:37:54,380
They said, “But what’s wrong in clothes.

552
00:37:54,380 --> 00:37:55,570
What is the need to have clothes?”

553
00:37:55,570 --> 00:37:56,750
I said, “That’s not the point!

554
00:37:56,750 --> 00:38:03,329
What I am saying if by becoming naked, if
you can become God, all the animals must go

555
00:38:03,329 --> 00:38:05,430
to God first, before you!”

556
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:08,980
You must understand what should happen to
you: is there should be a new dimension which

557
00:38:08,980 --> 00:38:09,980
must be enlightened within you.

558
00:38:09,980 --> 00:38:15,450
A new dimension must come into you.

559
00:38:15,450 --> 00:38:18,630
What about your own power: have you got you
own powers?

560
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:22,260
If you are spiritually evolved, you must have
your own powers.

561
00:38:22,260 --> 00:38:24,529
This is like enslavement.

562
00:38:24,529 --> 00:38:25,529
I said, “What are our own powers?”

563
00:38:25,529 --> 00:38:28,780
I said, “Can you tell in this person where
is the Kundalini?”

564
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:30,160
They said, “No, we don’t know.

565
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:31,569
We have never heard about it."

566
00:38:31,569 --> 00:38:33,599
“Can you tell what are your centres catching?

567
00:38:33,599 --> 00:38:35,200
Can you tell where are his centres rising?”

568
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,980
He said, “No, we cannot."

569
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:41,880
So I called him, I said, “Come along, have
your Realisation."

570
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:44,710
One of them I got hold of, somehow or other
brought him.

571
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:47,270
I think he was not interested in Realisation
at all.

572
00:38:47,270 --> 00:38:49,270
He was not at all interested.

573
00:38:49,270 --> 00:38:52,089
He was interested in exhibitionism.

574
00:38:52,089 --> 00:38:55,000
He wanted to exhibition himself in that Oxford
Street that’s why he went there.

575
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,000
Absolutely that’s true.

576
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,359
Otherwise, if he was, he would have said,
“All right, if you are saying ‘I am giving

577
00:38:57,359 --> 00:38:59,690
you Realisation,’ let me have it!”

578
00:38:59,690 --> 00:39:03,220
He said, “How can that be so silly?”

579
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:04,220
I said, “What silly?

580
00:39:04,220 --> 00:39:08,270
I said, “How can it be silly?”

581
00:39:08,270 --> 00:39:09,859
I said, “The wisest”.

582
00:39:09,859 --> 00:39:14,340
But must be somebody else is silly to see
things which are silly.

583
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:17,180
Like mad people: if you go to a lunatic asylum
they think you all are mad.

584
00:39:17,180 --> 00:39:24,920
Once our prime minister went to a lunatic
asylum and one lunatic came and started talking

585
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:25,920
to him very nicely.

586
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:26,920
He said, “How are you?

587
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:28,330
When did you come here?

588
00:39:28,330 --> 00:39:29,330
And who are you?”

589
00:39:29,330 --> 00:39:31,900
So he said, “I am Jawaharlal Nehru, I am
the prime minister of India."

590
00:39:31,900 --> 00:39:33,829
He said, “All right, all right, you’ll
be all right also.

591
00:39:33,829 --> 00:39:38,170
I used to say the same thing."

592
00:39:38,170 --> 00:39:39,440
(laughter)

593
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:43,549
But how do you judge whether you are right
or wrong?

594
00:39:43,549 --> 00:39:44,950
Where are you?

595
00:39:44,950 --> 00:39:50,190
The judgment comes when you have the dimension
to judge.

596
00:39:50,190 --> 00:39:52,260
When you are Realised you can judge.

597
00:39:52,260 --> 00:39:54,589
You can say what chakras are catching.

598
00:39:54,589 --> 00:39:59,760
When Self-realisation comes in, you know all
about these centres and you know all about

599
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:01,880
these channels; about yourself and about others.

600
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:06,039
The collective consciousness becomes an actualisation;
it becomes part and parcel of you.

601
00:40:06,039 --> 00:40:10,720
Like an egg when it gets transformed, you
really get a bird!

602
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:14,410
It’s not just “blah, blah, blah."

603
00:40:14,410 --> 00:40:18,930
You just get to see the bird with its wings
and everything.

604
00:40:18,930 --> 00:40:21,359
A transformation takes place.

605
00:40:21,359 --> 00:40:28,089
Your awareness must have that actual dimension
within itself, inside.

606
00:40:28,089 --> 00:40:33,430
Not outside by developing your some sort of
a horn or wearing some sort of a bushy hair.

607
00:40:33,430 --> 00:40:38,789
It’s something that happens to you within
where…(break in recording)…comes through

608
00:40:38,789 --> 00:40:42,650
when you start judging yourself.

609
00:40:42,650 --> 00:40:45,740
But God is compassion.

610
00:40:45,740 --> 00:40:47,289
He’s love.

611
00:40:47,289 --> 00:40:55,119
He gives you [the] chance, all the powers
to clear yourself and cleanse yourself.

612
00:40:55,119 --> 00:41:03,480
But nobody can help a person who is so dump
founded or mesmerised or who is such a, I

613
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:09,290
would say, unintelligent person; who doesn’t
understand that something has to happen to

614
00:41:09,290 --> 00:41:12,460
your awareness.

615
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:14,190
Then only you have achieved something.

616
00:41:14,190 --> 00:41:21,430
For days in and days out they are going and
going and going and achieving nothing.

617
00:41:21,430 --> 00:41:24,119
Somebody told me, “Oh, they are people who
love each other very much."

618
00:41:24,119 --> 00:41:25,119
“How do you know?”

619
00:41:25,119 --> 00:41:26,890
“They kiss each other quite a lot."

620
00:41:26,890 --> 00:41:28,319
I said, “What is there?”

621
00:41:28,319 --> 00:41:30,869
Any licentious society you find such kissing
going on.

622
00:41:30,869 --> 00:41:36,940
For example if you go to France, I mean, it’s
horrifyingly kissing society, I tell you.

623
00:41:36,940 --> 00:41:39,500
Everybody has a right to kiss everyone they
feel like.

624
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:42,079
I mean, it’s sometimes so much that you
really get frightened of the whole thing:

625
00:41:42,079 --> 00:41:44,589
anybody can come and kiss you, anybody is
supposed to…

626
00:41:44,589 --> 00:41:46,200
I mean, I don’t know how it works out but
it’s so.

627
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:47,200
So I said, “What is, so [great] in kissing?

628
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:48,200
There’s no love!”

629
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:57,990
Love is a thing which is not expressed in
that way, but which works, which flows.

630
00:41:57,990 --> 00:42:03,200
It’s a power which acts, just like the sun’s
rays.

631
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:05,619
Sun’s rays come and act on the leaves.

632
00:42:05,619 --> 00:42:13,299
In the same way the love flows and acts on
the Kundalini, and it gives Realisation to

633
00:42:13,299 --> 00:42:14,299
others.

634
00:42:14,299 --> 00:42:16,519
It transforms your life.

635
00:42:16,519 --> 00:42:18,980
You become a different person altogether.

636
00:42:18,980 --> 00:42:22,529
You become a master of yourself when you overpower
everything.

637
00:42:22,529 --> 00:42:29,950
Of course some are, I would call them, lame
people, so they need little more time.

638
00:42:29,950 --> 00:42:33,530
Some are very fast ones and some are so quick
that they once get it, they never lose it.

639
00:42:33,530 --> 00:42:41,890
And then the real growth of the new personality
starts in which you start enjoying that bliss

640
00:42:41,890 --> 00:42:43,089
which is promised.

641
00:42:43,089 --> 00:42:46,690
All that is said before has to be proved today
— every thing.

642
00:42:46,690 --> 00:42:55,410
Now like we went to one of the Protestant
Church meeting.

643
00:42:55,410 --> 00:42:57,880
I mean Catholics and Protestants and all sorts
of things, you know!

644
00:42:57,880 --> 00:43:01,130
I am facing, mullahs and priests and this
and that.

645
00:43:01,130 --> 00:43:02,890
But these people they said, “We believe
in Christ."

646
00:43:02,890 --> 00:43:03,890
I said, “Very good!

647
00:43:03,890 --> 00:43:07,490
That’s a very good thing to do, is to believe
in Christ, thank God.

648
00:43:07,490 --> 00:43:13,250
At least there is no anarchist or somebody
who is anti-Christ I am facing here!

649
00:43:13,250 --> 00:43:15,320
But,” I said, “where is Christ?”

650
00:43:15,320 --> 00:43:16,320
“He’s everywhere."

651
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:17,390
I said, “All right.

652
00:43:17,390 --> 00:43:18,960
But how do you contact Him?”

653
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:25,500
Everywhere there is ether, everywhere there
are pictures, everywhere there is music, but

654
00:43:25,500 --> 00:43:29,339
how do you get them in the television?

655
00:43:29,339 --> 00:43:30,539
How do you contact?

656
00:43:30,539 --> 00:43:37,450
He is placed in a centre within us and we
can prove it, through the Kundalini awakening,

657
00:43:37,450 --> 00:43:39,230
that Christ is there.

658
00:43:39,230 --> 00:43:44,460
Because when Kundalini reaches that centre,
the centre which is on the optic thalamus,

659
00:43:44,460 --> 00:43:49,789
which controls the pituitary and the pineal
body, [that], in that centre, resides Christ

660
00:43:49,789 --> 00:43:51,650
can be proved through Kundalini awakening.

661
00:43:51,650 --> 00:43:57,150
Because when Kundalini arrives at that point
and it does not pierce, you have to take the

662
00:43:57,150 --> 00:43:59,700
name of Christ and then Kundalini moves on.

663
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:04,099
But not the person who is not realised, the
one who is realised can only do it.

664
00:44:04,099 --> 00:44:08,480
So there are two types of people you find
in Sahaja Yoga, is the people who are realised

665
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:10,579
and those who are not realised.

666
00:44:10,579 --> 00:44:14,839
Now here the conflict starts that people who
are realised can shock other people because

667
00:44:14,839 --> 00:44:16,319
they say some things very positively.

668
00:44:16,319 --> 00:44:21,180
They say that, “See, this is wrong, you
should give up these things.

669
00:44:21,180 --> 00:44:23,550
This is not going to lead you anywhere."

670
00:44:23,550 --> 00:44:27,369
And they look just like as you are but they
know about your chakras.

671
00:44:27,369 --> 00:44:31,280
And when they tell you, you get angry with
them and half of them leave, but that’s

672
00:44:31,280 --> 00:44:32,280
not the way.

673
00:44:32,280 --> 00:44:33,690
One should know that they are just trying
to help you.

674
00:44:33,690 --> 00:44:37,339
