00:58:54,720 --> 00:58:58,890
they are placed on your fingers, where they
come, every thing you can know.

902
00:58:58,890 --> 00:59:01,529
It’s all inside not outside.

903
00:59:01,529 --> 00:59:04,280
And it should happen to all of you.

904
00:59:04,280 --> 00:59:07,440
After all I am here only for that job.

905
00:59:07,440 --> 00:59:12,920
I’ll work very hard, and I have been working
very hard, everyone knows that.

906
00:59:12,920 --> 00:59:16,049
But you have to also understand to co-operate
a little bit.

907
00:59:16,049 --> 00:59:17,049
Take your Realisation.

908
00:59:17,049 --> 00:59:20,450
After Realisation you will have to work hard
also.

909
00:59:20,450 --> 00:59:24,460
But before Realisation just leave it to people
who are realised.

910
00:59:24,460 --> 00:59:28,349
Like, when you don’t know swimming, it’s
better to leave it to people who know swimming.

911
00:59:28,349 --> 00:59:30,530
Once you learn swimming, you also teach others.

912
00:59:30,530 --> 00:59:33,250
There’s nothing like inferiority, superiority,
and all that.

913
00:59:33,250 --> 00:59:34,270
It’s not that.

914
00:59:34,270 --> 00:59:40,589
So just face it as simple people, not with
all this misidentification with ego.

915
00:59:40,589 --> 00:59:44,630
Now somebody was raising the Kundalini like
that, so one gentleman walked off, I said,

916
00:59:44,630 --> 00:59:45,630
“Why?”

917
00:59:45,630 --> 00:59:46,630
He said, “Why is he doing like this?”

918
00:59:46,630 --> 00:59:47,630
I said, “But you do not know."

919
00:59:47,630 --> 00:59:52,359
Supposing there is a person who is trying
to help you swimming, he puts his hand under

920
00:59:52,359 --> 00:59:55,430
your belly: you can get angry with that person,
“Why are you doing that?”

921
00:59:55,430 --> 00:59:56,630
I mean, he’s making you to float.

922
00:59:56,630 --> 00:59:58,289
But this is what it is.

923
00:59:58,289 --> 01:00:01,180
You do not know the technique which these
people know.

924
01:00:01,180 --> 01:00:06,080
You will also know the technique of Kundalini,
which is a living technique, because you are

925
01:00:06,080 --> 01:00:07,080
not yet living.

926
01:00:07,080 --> 01:00:11,162
When you become realised, you will be knowing
because the power will flow from your hand.

927
01:00:11,162 --> 01:00:15,039
You can feel it on your hands, the cool breeze
flowing.

928
01:00:15,039 --> 01:00:23,329
But there’s only one warning to all our
western seekers, which I always give: that

929
01:00:23,329 --> 01:00:27,980
you are great saints, I know you are seekers,
you are very genuine and you are honest, everything

930
01:00:27,980 --> 01:00:28,980
is there.

931
01:00:28,980 --> 01:00:33,359
But you have one defect is that you think
about everything.

932
01:00:33,359 --> 01:00:38,109
Even you have organised God, you have organised
about Him.

933
01:00:38,109 --> 01:00:42,839
You have already preconceived ideas about
Him — all this is there.

934
01:00:42,839 --> 01:00:46,249
And anybody who tries to play some tricks
with you, you are very happy with that person

935
01:00:46,249 --> 01:00:49,099
and you are going along with that person very
nicely.

936
01:00:49,099 --> 01:00:54,559
But here it is you who has to know, it is
you who has to achieve, it is you who has

937
01:00:54,559 --> 01:00:55,559
to judge.

938
01:00:55,559 --> 01:00:59,029
Nobody is going to say that you are all right
unless and until you say you are all right.

939
01:00:59,029 --> 01:01:01,510
It is you who have to believe into it.

940
01:01:01,510 --> 01:01:06,980
So what happens that after Realisation the
Kundalini rises and She pierces this fontanel

941
01:01:06,980 --> 01:01:09,150
bone area where you get your baptism.

942
01:01:09,150 --> 01:01:13,690
You can even feel the cool breeze coming from
your head, actually you can feel it.

943
01:01:13,690 --> 01:01:16,890
But then you forget the experience, you go
home and start thinking about it.

944
01:01:16,890 --> 01:01:20,651
As soon as you start thinking, the whole thing
comes down, because it is beyond thinking.

945
01:01:20,651 --> 01:01:25,500
The happening is beyond thinking: without
thinking it has happened.

946
01:01:25,500 --> 01:01:28,359
By thinking Kundalini doesn’t rise.

947
01:01:28,359 --> 01:01:30,980
So just allow it to work out.

948
01:01:30,980 --> 01:01:34,039
When it works out, you will be surprised [that]
it’s flowing.

949
01:01:34,039 --> 01:01:38,809
Supposing there is electricity coming and
the electricity comes in, you see the light

950
01:01:38,809 --> 01:01:39,809
flickering.

951
01:01:39,809 --> 01:01:43,910
If you start thinking about it, do you think
you’ll get back the light?

952
01:01:43,910 --> 01:01:44,910
No!

953
01:01:44,910 --> 01:01:46,900
You have to put the connection right.

954
01:01:46,900 --> 01:01:48,680
It’s something like that.

955
01:01:48,680 --> 01:01:52,779
So thinking gives you ramblings, people are
lost [in that].

956
01:01:52,779 --> 01:01:53,779
Then they come back.

957
01:01:53,779 --> 01:01:58,300
And once, after Realisation if you lose it,
it takes time, it takes time.

958
01:01:58,300 --> 01:02:00,950
It’s a headache to me and headache to you.

959
01:02:00,950 --> 01:02:03,019
Many people do that way but please don’t
do it.

960
01:02:03,019 --> 01:02:05,039
After all you are seekers of ages.

961
01:02:05,039 --> 01:02:09,630
Why should you waste your energy and time
and mine also.

962
01:02:09,630 --> 01:02:13,910
Be sensible and wise, get your Realisation
and get to it.

963
01:02:13,910 --> 01:02:15,849
Give up all your misidentifications.

964
01:02:15,849 --> 01:02:17,410
All these are misidentifications.

965
01:02:17,410 --> 01:02:22,779
And do not reach that point where you become
helpless and you have to give up these misidentifications.

966
01:02:22,779 --> 01:02:28,130
Because I told one person I told that, “Your
guru is not all right,” and he wouldn’t

967
01:02:28,130 --> 01:02:30,069
believe me, because his Void was catching.

968
01:02:30,069 --> 01:02:33,099
Then he got epileptic, he got sick, then he
came to me.

969
01:02:33,099 --> 01:02:35,489
It took me three months to work on him.

970
01:02:35,489 --> 01:02:41,259
So the whole process of emancipation is slowed
down, and that’s how you pull down the forces

971
01:02:41,259 --> 01:02:42,259
of Divinity.

972
01:02:42,259 --> 01:02:43,970
There are so many things one can say.

973
01:02:43,970 --> 01:02:49,249
As you know there are lectures and lectures,
and Douglas has so many tapes and in London

974
01:02:49,249 --> 01:02:51,109
itself I have done so much.

975
01:02:51,109 --> 01:02:57,019
And to understand why London and why England,
you better read “Milton” by William Blake.

976
01:02:57,019 --> 01:03:03,309
He has prophesied all this that is going to
happen.

977
01:03:03,309 --> 01:03:06,359
That England is going to be the Jerusalem.

978
01:03:06,359 --> 01:03:10,609
That it is going to be the pilgrimage.

979
01:03:10,609 --> 01:03:13,089
It has described everything that is Sahaja
Yoga.

980
01:03:13,089 --> 01:03:16,670
It’s a wonderful prophesy, you better read
it to understand.

981
01:03:16,670 --> 01:03:20,160
It is even described where the ashram would
be in Lambeth Vale.

982
01:03:20,160 --> 01:03:27,369
It has described that first it will start
in Surrey Hills where I first came and stayed.

983
01:03:27,369 --> 01:03:31,934
And he has described in the end how the Virgin
Herself is going to work it out, how the Mother

984
01:03:31,934 --> 01:03:33,180
is going to work it.

985
01:03:33,180 --> 01:03:34,380
It’s all beautifully done.

986
01:03:34,380 --> 01:03:39,259
So you had such a great poet like Blake, who
has already guided you.

987
01:03:39,259 --> 01:03:41,150
Better take guidance from them.

988
01:03:41,150 --> 01:03:46,720
Another is Shakespeare who was another great
realised-soul who showed the futility of nonsense

989
01:03:46,720 --> 01:03:49,749
of this so-called romanticism and all this.

990
01:03:49,749 --> 01:03:52,480
So be sensible about it, be wise.

991
01:03:52,480 --> 01:03:53,770
You have a great heritage.

992
01:03:53,770 --> 01:03:57,670
Your Stonehenge and all these things, I have
talked about it, what are these.

993
01:03:57,670 --> 01:04:01,720
This place has been worked out by many saints
before, and today you are born here.

994
01:04:01,720 --> 01:04:04,059
You are here to achieve your highest.

995
01:04:04,059 --> 01:04:06,599
There is a purpose behind it.

996
01:04:06,599 --> 01:04:13,960
As I said that England is the heart of the
universe, no doubt, it is the heart, that’s

997
01:04:13,960 --> 01:04:14,960
why I am here.

998
01:04:14,960 --> 01:04:16,510
I didn’t come as an immigrant or anything.

999
01:04:16,510 --> 01:04:20,299
I came because my husband got elected to this
post and I came here.

1000
01:04:20,299 --> 01:04:21,390
That was all organised.

1001
01:04:21,390 --> 01:04:25,710
And I am just there because of that, and you’ll
be happy to know he has been re-elected again

1002
01:04:25,710 --> 01:04:29,829
for five years so I am going to be here five
years more.

1003
01:04:29,829 --> 01:04:35,000
And then England being the heart, we have
to be very careful because everything articulates

1004
01:04:35,000 --> 01:04:39,140
through heart, and the Spirit lives in the
heart.

1005
01:04:39,140 --> 01:04:44,460
England is the heart, India is the Kundalini
and Europe is the liver.

1006
01:04:44,460 --> 01:04:51,530
Now see the contradiction: Kundalini, where
Kundalini is in India people are sleeping.

1007
01:04:51,530 --> 01:04:55,819
Kundalini is sleeping; where Europe, where
the liver is, where the attention is, people

1008
01:04:55,819 --> 01:05:00,890
are drunkards, they are drinking, the liver
is gone!

1009
01:05:00,890 --> 01:05:02,940
Where the heart is England, it is lethargic.

1010
01:05:02,940 --> 01:05:05,250
Tell me now: what am I to do?

1011
01:05:05,250 --> 01:05:12,279
This is the situation in which we are, so
we have to rise to the occasion and achieve

1012
01:05:12,279 --> 01:05:13,279
our goal.

1013
01:05:13,279 --> 01:05:17,829
England is very important, very, very important,
and I am going to work very hard here, no

1014
01:05:17,829 --> 01:05:18,829
doubt.

1015
01:05:18,829 --> 01:05:26,599
But you all have to help me and understand
that the time has come now to get what you

1016
01:05:26,599 --> 01:05:27,910
have been seeking.

1017
01:05:27,910 --> 01:05:36,180
All of you should achieve what you have been
seeking, right now.

1018
01:05:36,180 --> 01:05:41,720
May God Bless you.

1019
01:05:41,720 --> 01:05:43,849
I would like you to ask me some questions.

1020
01:05:43,849 --> 01:05:47,779
But don’t ask controversial questions like:
“I read in this book, that book…”

1021
01:05:47,779 --> 01:05:51,849
Then somebody has been to some far-fetched
place, “What do you think of this guru and

1022
01:05:51,849 --> 01:05:52,849
that guru?”

1023
01:05:52,849 --> 01:05:53,849
I am not going to get into controversies.

1024
01:05:53,849 --> 01:06:03,190
So don’t ask me about any guru, you will
find out yourself.

1025
01:06:03,190 --> 01:06:06,940
Ask some sensible questions about Realisation.

1026
01:06:06,940 --> 01:06:23,660
Seeker: If you feel yourself to be completely
blocked, if there’s nothing you can do.

1027
01:06:23,660 --> 01:06:28,119
What do you do?

1028
01:06:28,119 --> 01:06:36,019
Shri Mataji: You leave it to me.

1029
01:06:36,019 --> 01:06:38,380
I am quite a master in this.

1030
01:06:38,380 --> 01:06:40,470
I have had all kinds of blocks: mountains
after mountains.

1031
01:06:40,470 --> 01:06:42,489
You don’t know how much I have gone through.

1032
01:06:42,489 --> 01:06:44,930
I have become now an expert.

1033
01:06:44,930 --> 01:06:54,609
You are not such a block, at least as far
as you are concerned, so don’t worry.

1034
01:06:54,609 --> 01:06:56,819
You see, I have worked hard for years to study
all the permutations, combinations.

1035
01:06:56,819 --> 01:07:03,260
I used to enter into the Kundalini and into
the…to find out what are the blockages.

1036
01:07:03,260 --> 01:07:07,080
And I know how to find the way out.

1037
01:07:07,080 --> 01:07:09,849
You just leave it to me.

1038
01:07:09,849 --> 01:07:14,150
But later on when you get it, everything I
will tell you, every secret about it.

1039
01:07:14,150 --> 01:07:17,569
Everything I am going to tell you, and you
are going to become the master yourself.

1040
01:07:17,569 --> 01:07:22,309
That’s what it is.

1041
01:07:22,309 --> 01:07:26,230
What kind of blockage you are fearing?

1042
01:07:26,230 --> 01:07:31,249
Seeker: Some kind of fear.

1043
01:07:31,249 --> 01:07:39,289
Shri Mataji: Fear is very simple to conquer.

1044
01:07:39,289 --> 01:07:43,910
You see, it is because of conditionings.

1045
01:07:43,910 --> 01:07:49,119
People are … I don’t know why they do
it, this I cannot explain.

1046
01:07:49,119 --> 01:07:50,579
Human beings are very difficult.

1047
01:07:50,579 --> 01:07:54,789
Like in France they said, “Mother, if you
say you are a happy person, they’ll think

1048
01:07:54,789 --> 01:07:55,789
you are naïve."

1049
01:07:55,789 --> 01:07:56,789
I said, “Why?”

1050
01:07:56,789 --> 01:07:59,220
“Because [they think] you do not know any
problems.

1051
01:07:59,220 --> 01:08:01,880
So you have to be a very unhappy person.

1052
01:08:01,880 --> 01:08:03,190
You have to show you are unhappy.

1053
01:08:03,190 --> 01:08:06,720
Your cheeks must go inside like this; you
must look absolutely like a prisoner of Ceylon."

1054
01:08:06,720 --> 01:08:07,720
I said, “Really?”

1055
01:08:07,720 --> 01:08:12,779
They said, “If you go like this, Mother,
in such a happy mood, they will never take

1056
01:08:12,779 --> 01:08:13,779
you seriously!”

1057
01:08:13,779 --> 01:08:16,720
I said, “But I don’t think."

1058
01:08:16,720 --> 01:08:19,180
They said, “We must suffer.

1059
01:08:19,180 --> 01:08:21,150
That’s what they want."

1060
01:08:21,150 --> 01:08:23,100
I said, “But why?

1061
01:08:23,100 --> 01:08:27,310
Christ has suffered for you, now why do you
want to suffer?”

1062
01:08:27,310 --> 01:08:28,310
But they say these things.

1063
01:08:28,310 --> 01:08:30,290
Actually you know, it is with these people
I have seen they say.

1064
01:08:30,290 --> 01:08:37,240
I said, “If it is so, you are people having
prostitutes on the streets, lined up together.

1065
01:08:37,240 --> 01:08:39,930
You have pubs on the other side.

1066
01:08:39,930 --> 01:08:42,522
You have gay, this thing and nonsensical things
all over.

1067
01:08:42,522 --> 01:08:43,522
You are unhappy.

1068
01:08:43,522 --> 01:08:47,260
You are making everybody extremely unhappy."

1069
01:08:47,260 --> 01:08:51,770
I said, “I am unhappy because I see this
kind of thing going on here, and you are saying

1070
01:08:51,770 --> 01:08:52,770
that you are unhappy.

1071
01:08:52,770 --> 01:08:56,250
You are not unhappy at all, you are just escaping
it."

1072
01:08:56,250 --> 01:08:59,650
Also so the fear is another sort of a conditioning
on you.

1073
01:08:59,650 --> 01:09:05,380
It comes to you [such] that you think, “I
will have to lose something."

1074
01:09:05,380 --> 01:09:08,710
No, you blossom into something.

1075
01:09:08,710 --> 01:09:11,000
Because you are beautiful.

1076
01:09:11,000 --> 01:09:16,590
I see that beauty and I see that Spirit and
you are that.

1077
01:09:16,590 --> 01:09:22,010
And the fear that you have is because you
cannot see it.

1078
01:09:22,010 --> 01:09:23,010
It’s just a conditioning.

1079
01:09:23,010 --> 01:09:24,010
You just blossom into it.

1080
01:09:24,010 --> 01:09:26,640
Did you read any one of these horrible books
on Kundalini?

1081
01:09:26,640 --> 01:09:27,640
That’s it!

1082
01:09:27,640 --> 01:09:29,650
That’s very simple to overcome.

1083
01:09:29,650 --> 01:09:33,960
I’ll tell you what: a villager comes to
the city, he has never seen electricity and

1084
01:09:33,960 --> 01:09:35,010
he puts his two fingers in the plug!

1085
01:09:35,010 --> 01:09:36,010
[It’s] like that.

1086
01:09:36,010 --> 01:09:37,010
They are absolutely unauthorised.

1087
01:09:37,010 --> 01:09:40,310
You know, they do not know what Kundalini
is.

1088
01:09:40,310 --> 01:09:42,270
I was amazed.

1089
01:09:42,270 --> 01:09:46,750
There’s a big book like that, and he says
the Kundalini is in the stomach!

1090
01:09:46,750 --> 01:09:48,990
I said, “Now what to do?”

1091
01:09:48,990 --> 01:09:51,280
And he’s written a big book like that, you
see.

1092
01:09:51,280 --> 01:09:56,600
They are naïve first of all, they are unauthorised,
they are unholy.

1093
01:09:56,600 --> 01:09:57,610
Everybody cannot do Kundalini’s job.

1094
01:09:57,610 --> 01:10:02,460
You have to be an authorised person from God
and you have to be holy person.

1095
01:10:02,460 --> 01:10:08,140
Specially a gentleman, I know, who has written
a book, he leads such a horrible private life.

1096
01:10:08,140 --> 01:10:11,890
He’s such a money-minded fellow.

1097
01:10:11,890 --> 01:10:14,170
He talks of Kundalini, I was surprised.

1098
01:10:14,170 --> 01:10:18,840
He’s taking money from everyone and he’s
leading such a horrible life and he’s spoiling

1099
01:10:18,840 --> 01:10:21,200
women and doing all kinds of things and raping
them.

1100
01:10:21,200 --> 01:10:25,650
And he is telling that my Kundalini rose and
it troubled me like this, and it will.

1101
01:10:25,650 --> 01:10:30,210
Kundalini doesn’t trouble actually [it’s]
this Deity sitting there on the first chakra

1102
01:10:30,210 --> 01:10:31,230
– Shri Ganesha.

1103
01:10:31,230 --> 01:10:35,960
He is the Deity of innocence, who incarnated
as Jesus Christ.

1104
01:10:35,960 --> 01:10:40,410
He only thrashes such people who try to handle
Kundalini.

1105
01:10:40,410 --> 01:10:49,280
Even they try to put your innocence, which
looks after your sex onto the Mother.

1106
01:10:49,280 --> 01:10:54,700
Just imagine what a sinful thing it is.

1107
01:10:54,700 --> 01:10:58,720
Innocence is the one that is your special
power.

1108
01:10:58,720 --> 01:11:02,270
That’s why people are not even spontaneous
now in sex.

1109
01:11:02,270 --> 01:11:03,900
They just think about it.

1110
01:11:03,900 --> 01:11:17,390
Do you know the latest numbers of people who
are impotent in the West?

1111
01:11:17,390 --> 01:11:24,250
And do you know, in Switzerland itself, out
of five families only one family can produce

1112
01:11:24,250 --> 01:11:27,470
children – they are impotent.

1113
01:11:27,470 --> 01:11:31,610
If you think about sex, you can become impotent.

1114
01:11:31,610 --> 01:11:36,450
All the spontaneity is lost.

1115
01:11:36,450 --> 01:11:39,710
And here people are getting sophisticated
with it.

1116
01:11:39,710 --> 01:11:46,050
Either you become a rapist or you become absolutely
an impotent person.

1117
01:11:46,050 --> 01:11:51,120
Either you go the right or to the left.

1118
01:11:51,120 --> 01:11:59,680
So these people who talk about Kundalini have
no sense of proportion, they have lead a very

1119
01:11:59,680 --> 01:12:01,300
bad life, they are unholy people.

1120
01:12:01,300 --> 01:12:03,980
They have no sense of holiness, righteousness.

1121
01:12:03,980 --> 01:12:06,090
I mean righteousness is the thing.

1122
01:12:06,090 --> 01:12:11,020
When I talk of righteousness they think I
am a Victorian, you see.

